{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/react-setup-from-zero","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a2fafdb4-5693-5567-8fb9-cbf5c2a79976","html":"<p>最近工作不多，趁着有空，学习一下react。首先需要实现的是搭建开发环境。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code>是react官方Facebook推出的脚手架工具，可以一行命令实现生成一个标准的react项目——对初学者上手开发比较友好，但如果后期需要调整配置就需要完整理解配置的各个文件及其内容。</p>\n<p>所以准备用webpack配置一个开发环境，毕竟webpack用了很多年了😂。</p>\n<h2 id=\"target\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#target\" aria-label=\"target permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Target</h2>\n<p>一个react前端的开发环境，下面几项是必不可少的:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>react</li>\n<li>webpack</li>\n<li>jsx</li>\n<li>html</li>\n<li>css</li>\n<li>webpack-dev-server</li>\n</ul>\n<p>下面分别实现这几项。</p>\n<p>first in first，新建一个空目录并快速初始化<code class=\"language-text\">npm init -y</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"react\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react\" aria-label=\"react permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>react</h2>\n<p>项目引入react相关的包。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> react react-dom</code></pre></div>\n<p>创建<code class=\"language-text\">src/index.jsx</code>文件。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"webpack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack\" aria-label=\"webpack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack</h2>\n<p>作为前端web项目打包的工具，webpack（使用webpack 4）必不可少。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -D webpack webpack-cli</code></pre></div>\n<p>项目根目录新建<code class=\"language-text\">webpack.config.js</code>文件，并写入下面的内容。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// webpack.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  entry<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/index.jsx'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>加入<code class=\"language-text\">scripts</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  scripts<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"build\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"webpack --mode production\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>至此可以<code class=\"language-text\">yarn build</code>生成打包后的js文件了</p>\n<h2 id=\"编译jsx\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91jsx\" aria-label=\"编译jsx permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>编译jsx</h2>\n<p>webpack不支持jsx语法，需要引入babel实现代码的编译。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -D @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react babel-loader</code></pre></div>\n<p>根目录新建<code class=\"language-text\">babel.config.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"presets\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@babel/preset-env\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@babel/preset-react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>webpack加入babel-loader的支持</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// webpack.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// xxx</span>\n  module<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    rules<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        test<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/\\.(js|jsx)$/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        exclude<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/node_modules/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        use<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          loader<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"babel-loader\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// xxx</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// xxx</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>此时项目支持jsx的语法了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"编译html\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91html\" aria-label=\"编译html permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>编译html</h2>\n<p>web应用都需要html入口页，webpack默认不支持，需要使用<code class=\"language-text\">html-loader</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">html-webpack-plugin</code>实现html的读取和注入js bundle地址。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -D html-loader html-webpack-plugin</code></pre></div>\n<p>新建入口html页面文件<code class=\"language-text\">src/index.html</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- src/index.html --></span>\n<span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>set up React, Webpack, and Babel<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>修改webpack配置</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// webpack.config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> HtmlWebPackPlugin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"html-webpack-plugin\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  module<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    rules<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// xxx</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        test<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/\\.html$/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        use<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            loader<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"html-loader\"</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HtmlWebPackPlugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      template<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/index.html\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      filename<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./index.html\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>最后修改入口jsx文件内容</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/index.jsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Form <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./js/components/Form\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Form为任意写的一个组件</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> wrapper <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"container\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Form</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>这时，<code class=\"language-text\">yarn build</code>编译后就会生成最终的产物目录（<code class=\"language-text\">dist/</code>目录）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"编译css\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91css\" aria-label=\"编译css permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>编译css</h2>\n<p>css的接入方案有很多，以后再介绍各种用法。</p>\n<h2 id=\"webpack-dev-server\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack-dev-server\" aria-label=\"webpack dev server permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack-dev-server</h2>\n<p>前端本地开发离不开<code class=\"language-text\">webpack-dev-server</code>。接入比较简单，首先是安装依赖。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -D webpack-dev-server</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>再加入脚本即可。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  scripts<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// xxx</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"start\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"webpack-dev-server --open --mode development\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn start</code>就可直接打开开发环境了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"总结 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总结</h2>\n<p>总体上来说，手撸一个react的开发/编译环境是很简单的，且可以借这个机会熟悉webpack的配置。</p>\n<p>因为纯手撸，后续需要修改配置、优化编译等可以查阅webpack官网、而不需要额外的学习成本（<code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code>等）。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/react-setup-from-zero","tagSlugs":["/tag/react/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-10-13 22:00","description":"","tags":["react"],"title":"从零搭建react开发环境","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/react-setup-from-zero"}}}